{"tid":1380180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦已要求西方停武器供應直至有獨立調查","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:00:46.000Z","uid":82938,"like":278,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"5140cd8c54ec7017e53e07eac71f6199d29a2a71","tid":1380180,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】CNN：港警用美製催淚彈 國際特赦：西方應停武器供應直至有獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）周日報道，港警周日晚用於驅散中上環示威者的催淚彈，當中包括由美國製造的。而國際特赦組織促請西方社會暫停向港府提供武器，直至港府成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\nCNN記者從遺留地上催淚彈殼，發現催淚彈由美國賓夕凡尼亞州人群控制產品製造商「NonLethal Technologies」生產。<br />\n<br />\n另外，CNN記者又發現，警方用於驅散示威者的橡膠子彈，以大小和重量判斷，雖不足以致命，一旦被擊中卻也可造成相當痛楚。報道又指出，從社交網絡流傳的圖片所見，中彈記者和示威者胸部和手臂都呈現手掌大小的瘀痕。<br />\n<br />\n警方上周日於上環暴力清場後，已被國際特赦組織批評多次使用過度武力處理示威。國際特赦組織表示，正向美、英、德、法等地政府要求停止向港府供應水炮車、催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈、發射器等裝置，直至港府成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n英國國會上月25日宣佈停止向港發人群管理裝備出口許可證，直至香港人權及基本自由疑慮得到充份釋除。歐洲議會本月中亦通過決議案，要求歐盟成員國等實施技術出口管制工作，拒讓中國及香港取得「用作侵犯基本權利」技術。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190729/59873985?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59873985%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=97a585c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59873985%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6a29af67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190729/59873985?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"16b38f3f059a615431de540327583df4eec91dee","tid":1380180,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"Great"},{"pid":"e8ccc707d558495b655f4775d09a78e5d9e97e4f","tid":1380180,"uid":215876,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"終於有少少行動"},{"pid":"76555a2440787fc0007907b5b53bfc9b10037836","tid":1380180,"uid":27432,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"梗係要啦, 27,28號射左都唔知幾多百粒蛋,<br />\n外國掉晒汽油彈都無咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23deddc34427fed4541c53dc984c6b472bd28a47","tid":1380180,"uid":37666,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"唔該 快<br />\n香港就黎唔掂"},{"pid":"c054c2650bf9dda33731e9db4248e928d0329324","tid":1380180,"uid":10509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"cnn 幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e22d245e082c9ba0bdb2bc1827068ce0f475fd7","tid":1380180,"uid":285523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n【警告】唔好令今次運動瓦解於自己手中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378948</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要Fact Check<br />\n要用Telegram<br />\n<blockquote>Telegram channel 整合<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205184\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205184</a></blockquote><br />\n要包容及理性討論<br />\n唔好一味煽動情緒<br />\n切勿濫用加密</span></span>"},{"pid":"39d6d133a58f8767be50d5559898dcd56d9a6203","tid":1380180,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5工罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style