nk/h_16b8ac8ec3dbc98feba4d272ee10fefc</a><br />\n<br />\nEarlier this week, Amnesty International published a statement calling on other countries to halt sending these types of products to Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org.hk/en/immediate-suspension-of-supplies-of-less-lethal-crowd-control-equipment-to-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org.hk%2Fen%2Fimmediate-suspension-of-supplies-of-less-lethal-crowd-control-equipment-to-hong-kong%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b9ef42c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org.hk/en/immediate-suspension-of-supplies-of-less-lethal-crowd-control-equipment-to-hong-kong/</a><br />\n<br />\nAmnesty International is now mobilizing sections in the USA, UK, Germany, France and other sections around the world, calling their local authorities to suspend all transfers of less lethal &ldquo;crowd control&rdquo; equipment, including water cannon vehicles, tear gas, pepper spray, rubber bullets, projectile launchers and parts and components to Hong Kong, and maintain the suspension until the Hong Kong authorities put in place adequate safeguards including<br />\n1. A prompt, full, impartial, effective and independent investigations into all cases of human rights violations by police forces.<br />\n2. A fundamental change in guidance and practices are seen<br />\n3. Provide continuous and thorough professional human rights-based training for all officers required to carry out law enforcement duties"},{"pid":"266ba80570ab20b946376d061b09d36afd840611","tid":1380180,"uid":265507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4197423788a3381c4e2ca9b2645ce05842a050d5","tid":1380180,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6943470d92865270644f975782